N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4110.7 - Records

State Regulations
A record can be made only in a public race; the word must
be given by a licensed starter; the time must be taken by official timers, as
defined in section
4110.1
of this Part, and the record
of the race signed by the judges, timers and starter. Notes
